{"tid":583921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[HK01]  網傳國務院取消港澳通行證　廣東省公安廳闢謠","createTime":"2018-03-07T11:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T13:59:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6100ee1d84077fad517fdd7fff6b43333d4e33","tid":583921,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"近日網上瘋傳一張圖，圖上寫著：「經國務院批准，決定在2018年5月1日起，在廣東實驗試行取消港澳通行證，採用第二代身份證出境，逗留時間為7天，每次間隔為一個月。」<br />\n今天（3月6日）下午，廣東省公安廳闢謠，表示網傳消息是「假的！假的！假的！」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1256265/xlarge/b457e08c291c850bd1219e7f95fb452c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1256265%2Fxlarge%2Fb457e08c291c850bd1219e7f95fb452c.jpg&h=054cf703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日網上瘋傳在2018年5月1日起，在廣東實驗試行取消港澳通行證，唯官方回應這是謠言。（《南方都市報》）<br />\n不過在國務院港澳事務辦公室的官網上，並沒有這條消息。今天下午，廣東省公安廳透過官方微博平安南粵、深圳市公安局透過官方微博深圳公安發表回應闢謠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1256283/xlarge/400d953c14f1b04a69ddd7b386d24c72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1256283%2Fxlarge%2F400d953c14f1b04a69ddd7b386d24c72.jpg&h=a766840e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天下午，廣東省公安廳透過官方微博平安南粵發表回應闢謠。（《南方都市報》）<br />\n廣東省公安廳出入境政務服務網今天也發佈公告：近日，網上流傳關於「國務院取消港澳通行證」的謠言，廣東公安出入境提醒廣大群眾：目前沒有收到該方面通知。出入境相關信息，請以官方發佈為准，請勿盲目信謠傳謠！<br />\n<br />\n目前，內地居民前往港澳地區仍需要辦理港澳通行證及簽注。廣東省內居民可通過異地辦理、24小時「立等可取」自助辦證機等多種便捷方式辦理、更換通行證及續簽簽注。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，相似的謠言並非第一次傳播了。早在2011年4月，網絡上便流傳過「從5月1日開始，珠海戶口和深圳戶口過澳門、香港不用簽證，只需拿身份證就能過關」這樣一則消息。隨後，深圳公安發微博並冠以「闢謠」字樣，表示那是地地道道的假消息，民眾請勿輕信。<br />\n<br />\n（《南方都市報》）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/165720/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%BB%B3%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F165720%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%259C%2581%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E9%2597%25A2%25E8%25AC%25A0&d=yfStLp%2FTRVbgmmFJcqg0P8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=91071ec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/165720/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%BB%B3%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0</a>"},{"pid":"a17a44d33632284981647fe55e0ffea0bcaa5fb2","tid":583921,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"官方account都用&quot;表情包&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848c5f4ddbd1ba28f8bfb2df6463d7dfd4001b2f","tid":583921,"uid":38671,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:52:58.000Z","msg":"共媒放風試水溫"},{"pid":"29a220d4c69be04a740d5c38c41a3909a7d086d5","tid":583921,"uid":33796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"冇人反對，通過！"},{"pid":"eaf747ce5d7ec27c7f600a15c35d74048a1272b9","tid":583921,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"港澳通行證係收入來源之一"},{"pid":"7804240a07f1887e820879d59ae8f337b25491da","tid":583921,"uid":11001,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"沒有<br />\n沒有<br />\n沒有<br />\n沒有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">通過</span></span>"},{"pid":"63f64e14066634f850f5a302a1ff6601ca720c53","tid":583921,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T12:09:43